      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "很好，你还未忘记我，但你莫非忘了这是什么地方，居然要在这里开腹剖胴，你的胆子也未免太大了吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
