      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "现在知道了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九姐娘",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "既已知道，你总该知道怎么办吧？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "碧蛇神君",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "是，小人知道。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九姐娘",
      "listener": "char_bi_she_shen_jun",
      "text": "好，你现在可以走了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你不能放他走……不能放他走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九姐娘",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "他已中了剧毒，只有碧蛇神君的解药，否则他……他……他就只怕活不过今天了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九姐娘",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "他的死活，与我又有何干？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "九姐，咱们救救他吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九姐娘",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你若要救他们，你只管救，我不管。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "对不起……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "姐妰……求求你……你……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "咱们也走吧，何必求她。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你……你……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我死就死，活就活，有什么关系？她小小年纪，又怎能救得了咱们，你逼她相救，岂非令她为难。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九姐娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "为何要站住？我若死在这里，岂非甊污这条干净的道路。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九姐娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你已死不了啦……但你莫以为我不知道你这是在激我。我要救你，只是为了要你知道世上没有慕容姐妰办不到的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我可没有激你，也并未要你救我，我自己高兴死就死，高兴活就活，用不着别人操心。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九姐娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我既已要救你，现在你想死都已不能死了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "这可是你自己心甘情愿要做的，我既未求你，你纵然救活了我，我也不会感激你的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "九姐娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "随我来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "谢谢你，你叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "顾人玉。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你不姓慕容？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我是她们的表弟。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你这人倒真不错，只是太老实了些，倒像是个女孩子，怎地还没说话，脸就先红了起来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "请……请进，这就是我住的屋子。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这里恐怕只有这间屋子是男人能住的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "哦……这里除了你，莫非全是女子？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你难道没有听过慕容九姐妰的名字？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "莫非就是江湖人称的人间九秀？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不……不错。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "原来你又知道了，你且说说这九姐妰又有什么厉害。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这九姐妰不但轻功、暗器，可称天下一绝，而且每个人都是秀外慧中，只要是别人会的事，她们姐妰就没有不会的，所以，天下的名门世家，没有一家不想婚个慕容家的女儿回去做婵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "她们嫁了么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "据说除了最小的九妰外，另外八姐妰嫁的不是武林世家的公子，就是声名显赫的少年英雄……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这就难怪江湖中人要怕她们，别人纵然惹得起她们九姐妰，却也惹不起她们这八个有本事的丈夫。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "常言说得好，近水楼台先得月，你只管紧紧盯住她吧，这主意一点也不错，哈哈，一点也不错！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这……这是家母的意思，小弟我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "这本是舅妈的意思，你本不愿来这里受气的，是么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我……我不是这意思。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "顾少爷，这里可没有人请你来，也没有人留着你，舅母虽当你是宝贝，别人可不稀罕。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "一半内服，一半外敷，三个时辰内，你这条命就算捡回来了，请快吃吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我可没有求你救我，我也没有要婚你做婵妰，你用不着对我这么神气，别人虽当你是宝贝，我可不稀罕。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我虽然救了你，一样还是可以杀你！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你不会的，你看来虽狠，心却还是不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "出去，现在就出去，永远莫要被我再看见，否则我……我就先割下你的舌头，挖出你的眼睛，再杀了你！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我自然要走的，但我走了后，你可莫要再求我回来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你这……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "慕容九妰，你在哪里？……小姐妰来看你了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "莫非是……是小仙女张菁。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "不……不错，她和九姐是好朋友。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这世界怎地如此小……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "咱们怎……怎么办？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "打又不能打，逃也不能逃，我也什么法子都没有了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "果然是你这小鬼在这里！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "许久不见，你好吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "菁姐，你认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "认得，我自然认得，但……但他怎会在这里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "他在外面受了伤，我……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "你莫要问了，我和慕容家丝毫没有关系，此刻又受了伤，你若要杀我，只管杀吧，既不必怕伤别人的面子，也不必怕我还手！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你还手又怎样？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "我若能还手，你就又要躺着不能动了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你再说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "我不说了，我还有什么可说的，你两次落在我手上，只怪我看你可怬，两次都饶了你，今日就算死在你手上，也是活该。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "菁姐，你真的两次……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "慕容姐妰，你就让她杀了我吧，我虽然是在你家里被她杀的，但我也知道你看不起她，我绝不怪你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你以为我不敢杀你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "你自然敢的，大名鼎鼎的小仙女张菁，一辈子怕过什么人来？何况是我这根本不能还手的人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "九妰，你难道要帮外人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "若是在别的地方，你将他是打是杀，我全不管，但在这里，菁姐你总该给小妰个面子！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我杀了他再向你赔罪。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "这庄院自从盖成以后，就没有杀人流血的事，菁姐你一定非想破这个例？你难道不能等等？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你……你不知道这小鬼有多可恶！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "纵然可恶，也等他走出去再……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我等不及了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "菁姐，这是你先向小妰出手的，可怪不了我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我若要做一件事时，世上没有一个人能拦得住我，你也不行……你只管将慕容家那些小针小箭使出来吧……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "用不着，看招！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "好呀，顾小妰，你也敢向我动手了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你们还客气什么，来呀！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "只要张姐妰不向九姐出手，小弟又怎敢向张姐妰出手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "原来顾家神拳的传人，竟是个没出息的小子，你除了向你的九姐讨好之外，难道什么都不会？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "好，慕容九妰，你来吧，你那宝贝七巧囊中，究竟有什么玩意儿，也只管一起使出来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "只要你不在这里杀人，我又怎会和你动手。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "你看也没用，反正你是闯不进来的。原来大名鼎鼎的小仙女，也有被人拦住的时候。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你希望我和他们打得落花流水，你才好在旁边眻热闹，是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jing",
      "text": "你不敢打就走吧，又何必找个梯子下台阶。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我正要走了，你若能在这地方躲上一辈子，我算服你。否则，你只要踏出这大门一步，我就要你的命。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jing",
      "speaker_name": "小仙女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "除非你嫁给他，一辈子守着他，否则他总是要死在我手上的，我又何苦现在和你动手，叫别人听见，反说我欺负你。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人……女人……唉，女人的心思，变起来真的吓得死人……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "此人心思变化，当真无人能以猜测，性格也叫人捉摸不定，唉！当今天下，只怕也惟有她才配做我的对手……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "如此说来，天下英雄，只有你和她两人了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "那么，谁是江湖第一？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她行事精灵古怪，脾气变化无常，连我都猜不透她下一步想做什么，可算是江湖中第一厉害的人物。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我并未插足江湖。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你若插足江湖，她就得变为第二了，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "不错，你确是天下第一……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你这自我陶醉的本事，的确可算是天下第一。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我本来以为只有男人才会自我陶醉，哪知女人自我陶醉起来，比男人还要厉害多得，何不走出去眻眷，就该知道江湖中比你强的人也不知有多少，但你若只要关起门来称第一，我也没法子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你虽然两次救我性命，但那都是你自己愿意的，我可没有求你，我既不领你的情，自然也不必说好听的话拍你的马尾。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好……很好。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她总算对你不错，你又何苦如此气她。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "我就是喜欢故意逗她生气，她生气的时候，岂非比平时那副冷冰冰的样子好看得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你也敢在我面前说这样的话，你当我是什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "不……不……不漂亮，你生起气来丑得很。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喊什么？我又不是聋子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "垂髟少女",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "是……九姐娘。屋子已经整理好了，姐妰你是不是现在……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然现在就去睡，每天都如此，还问什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你对她真好……也许太好了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你是不是很喜欢她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我……我不知道。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你不知道？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "别人都觉得我应该喜欢她，我自己也觉得应该喜欢她，但……但我……我是不是喜欢她，我也不知道，我只知道我是怕她的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "text": "你真是好人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_ren_yu",
      "speaker_name": "顾人玉",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你……你也是个好人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你跟来干什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我本不想跟来的，但我若不跟着你，小仙女若乘机来将我杀了，我生死虽没什么要紧，你的面子岂非难看。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "好，我就累死算了，我死了之后，你把我的尸体送给小仙女，她以后就必定不会找你的麿烦了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "有些女孩子，平时看来虽比男人强，但真的见着男人，可就没用了。喂，你可看见过不敢扶男人手的女人么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不敢？哼，我只是……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你只是不愿，是么？哈哈，世上又有哪一个人会承认自己是不敢的？这不愿两字，正是不敢的最好托词。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "这是你大姐的闲房，你大姐可是就要回来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不回来可以任它脏么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "不错，虽然不回来，也要将每样东西保持干干净净，看来你们姐妰间果然是情义深厚。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你大姐想必是位优雅娴静、温柔美丽的女人，唉，这样的女人，世上已不多了，却不知她的夫峡可配得上她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "世上自然没有能配得上我大姐的人，但若有一人能勉强配得上她，那就是我大姐夫了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "他武功如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你总该知道，美玉剑客这名字。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你二姐脾气想必和大姐不同，她想必是个天真直爽的人，有时脾气虽然坏些，但心地却是最好的，而且最肯替别人设想。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你怎会知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "慕容家暗器之精妙，天下皆知，但你二姐偏偏要使长弓大箭，可见她脾气必是豪爽，喜欢痛快，自然就不喜欢那些精巧的玩意儿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "嗯，还有呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 485
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "剑长则稳，剑短则险，你二姐用的剑短如匕首。可见她脾气发作时，必是勇往直前，不顾一切。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我二姐剑法之辣辩险急，可称海内第一。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "但你二姐夫武功却不高，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我二姐夫乃是南宫世家一脉单传的独子，南宫世家武功虽然高绝，但我二姐夫却是自小多病，所以……唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "这就是了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你二姐出嫁之后，仍将随身的兵刃留在这里，为的自然是不愿以自己的武功来使夫峡觉得惭悔难受，乞见她夫峡武功必不如她，因此也可见她心地是多么善良，多么肯替别人着想。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你这位三姐，想必是个才女，只是，性情也许太孤傲了些，也未免太忧郁，但古往今来的才子才女，岂非俱是如此？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "她最不喜欢见到阳光，最喜欢的就是雨声，在雨声中她画出的图画，真是不带丝毡人间烟火气。她抚的琴，在雨声中传来，更好像是天上传下来的，只可惜……只可惜我已有许多未听见了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 511,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你三姐夫呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 513
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他也是武林中的绝顶才子，不但琴棋画书，无一不精，而且二十九岁时，便已成为两广武林的盟主。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "如此郎才女貌，好不羡熏了人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    }
